{"tid":1229363,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"急！人在險地！想知道宜家情況！","createTime":"2019-06-16T02:16:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T02:41:01.000Z","uid":4464,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ff53447c372cf4defefc2093f25e93e020681e9","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"發夢見到自己係一個開po好危險嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢入面我有個細佬妹同我講話佢想去某個地方獻花。<br />\n<br />\n我宜家好擔心佢，想知個個地方宜家情況如何！<br />\n<br />\n夢入面有好多好可怕嘅烏龜，去獻花會唔會有危險！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位手足幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5137e01717f6505c5696cae5754c88b90d1825f2","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea42e23074f828df69e4e9bb4e1b9a9f1d78fd53","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:18:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"9e2ee134beeb058304fe342d687a2c99443c753d","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"去獻花有d咩要注意！"},{"pid":"5133e4a83eea1b0be30b542c9f88b24e3aebc56d","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:19:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"95c8aeed01df1756ada8453e89957ce595d819d4","tid":1229363,"uid":47112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:20:14.000Z","msg":"好撚安全的"},{"pid":"f3af19bfacfa090640a69f95318462add8b8ab62","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:21:27.000Z","msg":"使唔使帶裝備！"},{"pid":"b1a164542deac576e6ff8ac7eb1aa7350295daf0","tid":1229363,"uid":4464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:23:56.000Z","msg":"push"